<view class="customs-page">
  <view class="bg-watermark" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg class="watermark-svg" viewBox="0 0 240 240">
      <path d="M38 18 L78 14 L110 34 L146 30 L184 46 L206 84 L186 114 L198 142 L172 178 L132 206 L96 198 L76 170 L48 162 L34 130 L20 94 L30 62 Z" fill="none" stroke="#2D2D2D" stroke-width="2"></path>
      <path d="M56 64 L94 54 L132 68 L158 96 L146 130 L116 152 L84 144 L62 116 Z" fill="none" stroke="#2D2D2D" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
    </svg>
  </view>

  <scroll-view class="customs-scroll" scroll-y="true" show-scrollbar="false">
    <view class="hero-section">
      <view class="back-btn" bindtap="onGoBack">
        <view class="back-arrow"></view>
      </view>
      <view class="lang-tag">官方语言 / Official Language: 法语 (French)</view>
      <text class="hero-title">刚果(金) 风俗与禁忌指南</text>
    </view>

    <view class="bento-grid">
      <view class="card card-half">
        <text class="card-title">行为红线</text>
        <view class="bullet-row">
          <view class="icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">✋</view>
          <text class="bullet-text">忌用左手递物/进食</text>
        </view>
        <view class="bullet-row">
          <view class="icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">👤</view>
          <text class="bullet-text">忌触摸他人头部</text>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="card card-half">
        <text class="card-title">颜色避雷</text>
        <view class="swatch-row">
          <view class="swatch swatch-white"></view>
          <view class="swatch swatch-blue"></view>
          <view class="swatch swatch-black"></view>
        </view>
        <text class="swatch-text">忌纯白/大面积白（哀悼） | 忌纯蓝（殖民记忆） | 忌纯黑（丧色）</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="card card-full">
      <text class="card-title">宗教禁忌（必看）</text>
      <view class="bullet-row">
        <view class="icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">⛪</view>
        <text class="bullet-text">周日多为安息日，避免安排正式商务/公务活动。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="bullet-row">
        <view class="icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">👕</view>
        <text class="bullet-text">进入教堂须保守着装（禁短裤、无袖），保持安静。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="bullet-row">
        <view class="icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">🤲</view>
        <text class="bullet-text">严禁左手递物与进食，勿触摸他人头部。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="bullet-row">
        <view class="icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">📷</view>
        <text class="bullet-text">部族地区不可随意拍摄酋长与祭祀仪式，需先获许可。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="bullet-row">
        <view class="icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">🗣️</view>
        <text class="bullet-text">避免公开争论宗教冲突、批评宗教领袖或亵渎圣物。</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="card card-full dress-card">
      <text class="card-title">着装规范 (严格执行)</text>
      <view class="dress-layout">
        <view class="dress-col">
          <text class="dress-title">男士 👔</text>
          <text class="dress-text">商务需深色西装+领带；日常以T恤+长裤为宜，禁短裤/拖鞋/运动鞋。</text>
          <text class="dress-sub">部族/宗教场景避免纯白、纯蓝、纯黑及夸张撞色。</text>
          <view class="taboo-pill">
            <text class="taboo-icon">⚠️</text>
            <text class="taboo-label">绝对禁忌：迷彩/军绿色、矿区化纤衣物</text>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class="dress-col">
          <text class="dress-title">女士 👗</text>
          <text class="dress-text">商务宜过膝长裙/长裤套装；日常避免过短、透视、露肩。</text>
          <text class="dress-sub">部族/宗教场景建议包头巾、妆容朴素，避免浓妆。</text>
          <view class="taboo-pill">
            <text class="taboo-icon">⚠️</text>
            <text class="taboo-label">绝对禁忌：无袖、短裙、紧身露肩、公开亲密着装</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="card card-full">
      <text class="card-title">社交礼仪</text>
      <view class="chip-row">
        <text class="chip">称呼长辈：Papa / Mama / Chef</text>
        <text class="chip">正式称呼：先生/夫人/女士/小姐</text>
        <text class="chip">最高礼仪：举右手（掌心向外）喊“玛斯特”</text>
        <text class="chip">进教堂/酋长住所常需脱鞋</text>
      </view>
      <text class="etiquette-text">见面多行握手礼（轻柔且稍久），熟人可拥抱+轻拍后背；对长辈或酋长常以弯腰/半跪致意。男性不主动与女性握手，宜等待对方先示意。</text>
    </view>

    <view class="card card-full">
      <text class="card-title">特殊习俗（当地高频）</text>
      <view class="sub-title">丧葬习俗</view>
      <text class="bullet-text">11月1日为逝者节；部分部族有白蚁巢葬、树葬等传统，整体以土葬为主，忌火葬。</text>
      <view class="sub-title">婚俗与家庭</view>
      <text class="bullet-text">部分部族存在一夫多妻传统；彩礼可为货币、牲畜或劳动抵偿，婚礼常持续10-15天。</text>
      <view class="sub-title">日常交往</view>
      <text class="bullet-text">主食fufu常用手抓食；公开场合严禁亲吻等亲密行为；OK手势常被视为侮辱；部分家庭忌女婿触碰岳母。</text>
    </view>

    <view class="card card-full">
      <text class="card-title">官方信息来源</text>
      <text class="source-line">人民日报海外版（社交礼仪/着装）：http://paper.people.com.cn/rmrbhwb/html/2016-08/20/content_1705671.htm</text>
      <text class="source-line">中国驻刚果（金）大使馆（领事提醒/禁忌）：https://cd.china-embassy.gov.cn/chn/lsfw_0/lsbh_138072/laxz/</text>
    </view>

    <view class="page-gap"></view>
  </scroll-view>
</view>
